snippet.title: Lucid Trips | Unity Vision Summit 2016 Teaser
snippet.description:
Latest footage of our VR exploration game "Lucid Trips"... This version of the project will be exhibit at the Unity Vision Summit 2016. Lucid trips is nominated in the category "Best artistic achievement".
